OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Employees will be given the right to   
OL,6, ask for flexible working from their    
OL,7, first day at a new job, the government 
OL,8, has proposed.                          
OL,10,FNew legislation will mean that workers 
OL,11,Fwill not have to wait for 26 weeks to  
OL,12,Fseek flexible arrangements, as set out 
OL,13,Funder the current law.                 
OL,15,FThe government also wants to introduce 
OL,16,Flaws that make it easier for people on 
OL,17,Flow incomes to get a second job.       
OL,19,FHowever, the Trades Union Congress said
OL,20,Fthe government must go "much further". 
